  "description": [
    "Gestapo Aide in Paris Heralding Intensified Repression by Nazis Heydrich in Charge Made Reputation With Terrorism of Czechs By PAUL GHALI foreign Correspondent of The Star and Chicago Daily News Inc BERN May 8Even more inten sified Nazi repression in Western European countries is forecast with the arrival in Paris of Reinhard Heydrich Gestapo Chief Heinrich Himmlers assistant as announced in a Berlin dispatch to the Neue Zuercher Zeitung Hitherto the military police in Prance who lealt with numerous sabotage cases and murder attempts by socalled Communists have been under purely military leadership Prom now on the repression of troubles will be entirely in the hands of the Gestapo and the S S Elite Guard says the Zeitung Heydrichs arrival in Paris was preceded by a reorganization of j the Paris police which has now been adorned by a special German Ges tapo section headed by Prince von Waldeck noted S S member Hit ler has now ordered the Neue Zuercher Zeitung dispatch says that all Insurrection be combated with out mercy It is foregone here that presence of Himmlers aide in Paris means that this order will be ade quately carried out Terrorized Czechoslovakia Heydrich made his reputation as"
